  # Admin Analytics RPC Functions
  
  ## Purpose
  Provide system-wide analytics for admin dashboard using existing public_quiz_runs table.
  
  ## Functions Created
  
  1. get_admin_overview_stats()
     - Total plays all time
     - Plays this month
     - Active schools
